thread.title_full: Spa Store Australia reviewed by Michael

author: Michael
title: Michael
text: I live in Canberra and ordered products for my spa online. The prices are reasonable with free postage. They were delivered within 2 days, no fuss. I also called the staff about products in stock and they were very helpful, polite and new their business. Recommend Spa Australia to all, no matter where you live in Australia!
